            "title": "李寧盈利倒退2.6%派息增12.7%  股價曾升逾13%現升逾8%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">李寧(02331)早市大升，最高見22.38元，按年升13.32%，現升8.05%，報21.34元，成交5.06億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"李寧官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/02331-Web5.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"李寧官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/02331-Web5.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">李寧官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公司昨晚公布全年業績，2025年權益持有人應佔淨溢利為29.36億元(人民幣，下同)，按年減少2.56%，每股基本收益113.91分，派末期息每股23.36分，增加12.7%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">李寧收入295.98億元，按年升3.22%。整體毛利率為49%，下降0.4個百分點，公司稱︳主因在於渠道結構調整，直面消費者的渠道收入佔比下 降，以及直營促銷競爭加劇導致集團加大了折扣力度，使得毛利率略有下降。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">特許經銷商渠道收入按年增長6.3%，佔比進一步提升至46.6%；電商渠道收入提升5.3%；直營店舖佈局調整和消費場景轉移使得零售渠道表現承壓，收入下降3.3%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15765358-%e6%9d%8e%e5%af%a7%e7%9b%88%e5%88%a9%e5%80%92%e9%80%802-6%e6%b4%be%e6%81%af%e5%a2%9e12-7-%e8%82%a1%e5%83%b9%e6%9b%be%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be13%e7%8f%be%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be8",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/02331-Web4.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-20 10:26:35",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "小米曾插逾6%  新版SU 7較預售價低1萬人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">小米(01810)今早低見34.12元，跌6.06%，現跌5.62%，報34.28元，成交31.09億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：小米汽車微博\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260319_FI_source-web_01810-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：小米汽車微博\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/03/20260319_FI_source-web_01810-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：小米汽車微博</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">小米創始人兼董事長雷軍在「春季新品發布會」上宣布，新一代智能電動車小米SU7售價21.99萬元(人民幣‧下同)起。標準版售價21.99 萬元、Pro 版24.99 萬元、Max 版30.99 萬元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">公司早前公布的標準版售價22.99 萬元、Pro 版25.99 萬元、Max 版30.99 萬元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新一代SU7共有四大色系，九款外飾顏色，主駕全系標配18向可調運動座椅；全系搭載V6s Plus超級電機，Max版零百加速3.08s，最高時速265km/h。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15765270-%e5%b0%8f%e7%b1%b3%e6%9b%be%e6%8f%92%e9%80%be6-%e6%96%b0%e7%89%88su-7%e8%bc%83%e9%a0%90%e5%94%ae%e5%83%b9%e4%bd%8e1%e8%90%ac%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/20260107_FI_source-web_01810.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-20 09:55:48",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
