            "title": "A股向好  創板升逾1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">A股向好，滬股開市偏軟，其後向上，深股及創板均報升。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">上證指數開報4004點，跌0.05%或2點。現升11點或0.3%，報4018。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開盤報14021點，升0.86%或120點。現升183點或1.32%，報14081。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">創業板指開報3362點，漲1.6%或53點，現升74點或2.27%，報3384。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300開報4602點，漲0.43%或19點。現升37點或0.8%，報4619。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15765218-a%e8%82%a1%e5%90%91%e5%a5%bd-%e5%89%b5%e6%9d%bf%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-16.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-20 09:41:34",
